volunteer_experiences.description:
1) Ad-hoc officer at Municipality Hall in assisting BSN registration and Immigration&Naturalisation (IND) procedures i.e. getting a residence permit for the highly-skilled expatriates from all around the world;

2) Questions handling and providing advice to highly-skilled expatriates pertaining to the relocation process into The Netherlands e.g. getting residence permits, subscribing to mandatory health insurance, renting/buying a house, opening bank accounts, dutch language training, getting/converting driving license and more;

3) Content creator for expat newsletters on Dutch cultures and events;

4) Maintained the website and social media accounts;

5) Organized expats’ activities i.e. monthly Expat Meet & Greet, International Job Fair in Amsterdam, TwentseWelle Museum tour, Grolsch Brewery tour, Kaamps Cheese Farm Workshop & Tour; and 

6) Marketing activities to the international companies and expats community in the Twente region.
